# Dense UI System (Agent MUST follow)

**Goal**: Same business interaction → same shared UI primitive. Change tokens/components once → all adopters upgrade together. Users get a consistent monitoring-console experience.

**Authoritative docs**: `docs/DENSE_UI.md` (overview) · `src/components/data-display/` (implementation)

## Layer stack (do not skip layers)

1. **Tokens** — `src/index.css` (`--text-dense`, `--text-dense-meta`, `--table-cell-py/px`)
2. **Primitives** — `@/components/data-display` (tables, PnL, segments, icon actions, collapsible groups)
3. **Generic UI** — shadcn/ui (`Button`, `Dialog`, `Select`, …)
4. **Domain** — page-specific columns, hooks, API wiring only (minimal styling)

## Mandatory mapping (same interaction → same primitive)

| Interaction | Use | Never |
|-------------|-----|-------|
| Data table | `DenseDataTable` + head/row/cell | `ledgerTable` / `optTable` / `replay-*` / new `*.module.css` tables |
| Numeric columns | `denseTableNumCell` or `PnlCell` | Ad-hoc `text-right` without `font-mono tabular-nums` |
| PnL color (realized) | `pnlColorClass` / `InlinePnl` / `PnlCell` → `text-profit` / `text-loss` tokens | `pnl-positive`, module `.pnlPositive`, inline green/red hex, raw `text-emerald-*` / `text-red-*` |
| PnL color (unrealized) | `unrealizedPnlColorClass` → `text-unrealized` (site-wide yellow) | Green/red for unrealized values |
| Row icon actions | `IconActionButton` | Hand-rolled 20×20 buttons, `.iconBtn`, `window.confirm` |
| Expand row | `ExpandToggleCell` + `DenseTableDetailRow` | Unicode ▶/▼ in module CSS |
| Expand must not shift columns | `DenseDataTable` + `<colgroup>` + `denseTable.detailCellClip` | Detail rows without colgrid / wide content setting width |
| Identity column (Stock / Option entity) | `denseTableEntityCell` + `denseTableEntityLink` or `strong` + `text-entity-symbol` | `truncate` / Tag pill in Stock identity column |
| Segment / Include-Exclude | `SegmentControl` / `IncludeExcludeToggle` | New pill CSS in page modules |
| Stock link cell | `SymbolLinkButton` / `DenseLinkButton variant="stock"` | Custom link pill CSS per page |
| Nested strategy/instance panel | `CollapsibleGroup` (+ `CollapsibleBucketHeader`) | `strategyGroup` / `instanceHeader*` module classes |
| Nested sub-table | `NestedDenseTable` | Inline `<table className={styles…}>` |
| Detail fill rows | `DenseTableSubheadRow` / `DenseTableDetailRow` | `.ledgerDetailRow` module CSS |
| Empty / section title | `denseTable.emptyHint` / `denseTable.sectionTitle` + `denseTable.sectionBlock` | Page-local empty hint CSS |
| Execution source label | `ExecSourceBadge` | Hand-rolled Badge / ledger `sourceBadge` CSS per page |
| Stock identity column | `DenseLinkButton variant="stock"` or `strong` + `text-entity-symbol` | Tag pill in grid Stock column, custom link CSS |
| Stock highlight (secondary contexts only) | `DenseTag variant="symbol"` | Tag in Stock identity columns |
| Option contract link (Entity) | `DenseLinkButton variant="option"` (`--color-entity-option`) | Raw `text-sky-*` per page; Option Category tags for contracts |
| Fixed Income / Cash-like entity (tabs, legends) | Planned `--color-entity-fixed-income` / `--color-entity-cash-like` tokens | Position Category purple; inline amber/violet hex |
| Option Category — Strategy / Instance | `DenseTag variant="strategy" / "instance"`, `DenseLinkButton variant="strategy" / "instance"` | Ad-hoc colors; using for option contract strings |
| Option Category — Opportunity / Structure | Planned variants (token pending) | Ad-hoc colors per page |
| Position Category (watchlist / portfolio / user names) | Cell: `DenseTag variant="category"` · filter: `DenseTagButton` + `denseEntityFilterChipClass` (gray default, colored when selected) · **Group header**: `GroupHeaderRow variant="category"` | Gray generic pills without selected-state entity color; DenseTag pill on group header row |
| New business color | Add `--color-*` token in `src/index.css` (light + dark + `@theme`) first | Inline hex / raw palette classes in pages |
| Destructive confirm | App `ConfirmDialog` pattern | `window.confirm` / `window.alert` |

## Agent workflow (every UI change)

1. Read `docs/DENSE_UI.md` and grep `data-display` for an existing primitive before writing styles.
2. Implement with **components + tokens**, not new module CSS—unless the exception list applies.
3. Do **not** add page-local `*Classes.ts` for patterns already in `data-display`; extend the primitive instead.
4. Avoid overriding primitives with large `className` stacks; use `variant` or extend the shared component.
5. After UI edits run: `npm run lint && npm run build && npm run check:legacy-css`.
6. Validate visual semantics against the living contract page: **Settings → Configuration → UI Design System** (`/settings/ui-design-system`, `src/pages/settings/UiDesignSystemPage.tsx`) — PnL green/red/yellow; Entity (Stock/Option/FI/Cash-like); Option Category (Instance/Strategy/Opportunity/Structure); Position Category (watchlist/portfolio); status tags; density samples. Use **Copy Prompt** per section for scoped Agent fixes.

## Allowed CSS exceptions (narrow)

- Chart geometry: `PositionsChartsSection.module.css`, `DonutChart.module.css`, payoff SVG layout in `riskProfile.module.css`
- Toolbar/summary bars **until migrated** — do not copy their patterns into new pages
- No new `*Legacy.css`, no `:global()` in module CSS, no side-effect `import './x.module.css'`

## Extending the system

When a pattern repeats **≥3 times** across pages: add to `src/components/data-display/`, export from `index.ts`, document in `docs/DENSE_UI.md`, add a guard in `scripts/check-legacy-css.sh` if needed.

## Cross-skill

- New page visual direction: also read `.cursor/skills/frontend-design/SKILL.md` (Bifrost + Skote section).
